title: I can't see or interact with my Club (I'm the Club owner)
body:
Soon after the Clubs feature was released I started a club for myself and some friends. Sometime after the new client was released the game started acting like I wasn't in a club. I thought the club got disbanded of something, but on on of my alt accounts that's in the club too, It still shows the club and on the roster still shows my main (this account) as the Leader/Owner of it. Any help would be appreciated.

NA server
Club Name: League of Rednecks
Club Tag LoRnk

replies.body: Your club might have been out of sync, but I booped it for you.  Relog and let me know if everything looks okay now!
